name: Preeker Ranch (Hell Delivery)
description:
A simple ranching game where you farm little creeper-like slimes which would  explode when you get too close. 

Product for Ludum Dare 49. Made by XuanXuan, Jonathan Zhang, HenryTexas,  Zhang Dingxin, and Jiao Yue. 

*See the jam version: https://voyagerix.itch.io/preeker-ranch

*Has been transferred from personal account to group account.
